FirstExecutionFrom.Description: The start date for objects to import in the first flow run. Epoch or ISO timestamp format is supported.

Object.Description: The name of the object to pull from the data source.

ScheduleExpression.Description: How often the data should be pulled from data source.

Key.Description: A key to identify the tag.

Value.Description: Corresponding tag value for the key.

Name.Description: The name of the data integration.

ScheduleConfig.Description: The name of the data and how often it should be pulled from the source.

Tags.Description: The tags (keys and values) associated with the data integration.

ClientAssociationMetadata.Description: The metadata associated with the client.

ClientId.Description: The identifier for the client that is associated with the event integration.

EventBridgeRuleName.Description: The name of the Eventbridge rule.

EventIntegrationAssociationId.Description: The identifier for the event integration association.

Key.Description: A key to identify the metadata.

Value.Description: Corresponding metadata value for the key.

Key.Description: A key to identify the tag.

Associations.Description: The associations with the event integration.

Name.Description: The name of the event integration.
